---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import HorizontalCard from "../components/HorizontalCard.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title = "Projects" sideBarActiveItemID="projects">
  <div>
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold mb-5">My Portfolio Projects</div>
  </div>

  <HorizontalCard
    title="Sales Insights of AtliQ Hardware"
    img="/sales analysis.png"
    desc="A compact sales dashboard has been created to assist the sales director. It provides essential insights into company sales while minimizing space usage. This allows the director to easily track and analyze sales performance, facilitating informed decision-making."
    url="https://github.com/kirannavale/Portfolio-Projects/tree/main/AtliQ%20Hardware%20Sales%20Analysis"
    badge="Open on Github"
  />
  <div class="divider my-0"></div>
  <HorizontalCard
    title="PWC Virtual Internship Power Bi Projects"
    img="public/PWC.png"
    desc="I have successfully developed three powerful dashboards using Power BI. These dashboards include the Call Center Customer Dashboard, Telecom Churn and Retention Analysis Dashboard, and the Diversity and Inclusion Dashboard."
    url="https://github.com/kirannavale/Portfolio-Projects/tree/main/PWC%20Call%20Centre%20Trends%20Dashboard"
    badge="Open on Github"
    />
  <div class="divider my-0"></div>

  <HorizontalCard
    title="SQL Project - Music Store Analysis"
    img="public/mysqql.jpg"
    desc="By utilizing SQL, I extracted valuable insights and answered ad-hoc questions pertaining to the store's operations and customer behavior. This allowed me to analyze data efficiently and provide concise answers to specific queries. It helped better understanding of the store's performance and customer preferences."
    url="https://github.com/kirannavale/Portfolio-Projects/tree/main/SQL%20Music%20Store%20Analysis"
    badge="Open on Github"
  />
  <div class="divider my-0"></div>
  <HorizontalCard
    title="Python Project - Diwali Sales Analysis"
    img="public/python.png"
    desc="By leveraging Python's data analysis capabilities,These insights will help identify patterns, trends, and customer preferences. Ultimately, the analysis will facilitate informed decision-making to optimize sales performance and maximize revenue during the Diwali period."
    url="https://github.com/kirannavale/Portfolio-Projects/tree/main/Python%20Diwali%20Sales%20Analysis"
    badge="Open on Github"
  />
 
</BaseLayout>
